     V A L L E Y    M E T R O


   Valley Metro provides public transit service for the greater Phoenix,
   Arizona metropolitan area.





   CONTACT US

   We welcome your feedback!

   We want to hear your complaints, compliments, questions, suggestions.

   To help us serve you best, please contact the appropriate person from
   the list below.
     * VALLEY METRO BUS SERVICE--CUSTOMER SERVICE:
       ldickson@vm.maricopa.gov

     * Valley Metro Regional Dial-a-Ride Service:
       gbretz@valleymetro.org

     * Valley Telework Project:
       stierney@valleymetro.org

     * Valley Connections Light Rail Project:
       rail@valleyconnections.com

     * Valley Metro Transit Planning:
       tcollins@valleymetro.org

     * Valley Metro Rideshare/Trip Reduction Program:
       jreid@valleymetro.org

     * Valley Metro Website:
       webmaster@valleymetro.org

